DECORATE

Usage: ^gDECORATE^n

Decorate is used to customize the room description of your apartment.
All text pasted after will become the new room description, this will
save through reboot and copyover, but not in an event of the world
files being updated from another source. To finish entering the
description put @ on a blank line.

^WSee also: HOUSES^n

^GNote:^n Furniture merchants sell frames/paintings you can name (for display at home). Ask around decor shops for options.
